OL,6,FA Royal Navy sailor jailed in Bahrain
OL,7,Fhas been granted a royal pardon by the
OL,8,Fcountry's King.
OL,10,FOwen Haggerty, from Johnstone in
OL,11,FRenfrewshire, Scotland, was sentenced
OL,12,Fto three months behind bars last month
OL,13,Fafter reportedly trying to break up a
OL,14,Fstreet brawl.
OL,16,FThe Daily Record newspaper reported
OL,17,Fhis mother Kirsty Reynolds wrote to
OL,18,Fthe King of Bahrain, Hamad bin Isa Al
OL,19,FKhalifa, asking for a royal pardon for
OL,20,Fher son.
