OL,6,FShe said she "burst out crying" when
OL,7,Fshe was given the news that the pardon
OL,8,Fhad been granted.
OL,10,FMs Reynolds told the newspaper: "I
OL,11,Fcan't stop shaking. It is unbelievable
OL,12,Fnews, it is just such a massive hurdle
OL,13,Fthat we have overcome in the fight to
OL,14,Fbring Owen home."
OL,16,FPaisley and Renfrewshire South Labour
OL,17,FMP Johanna Baxter said she was "very
OL,18,Fpleased that he has been granted a
OL,19,Froyal pardon by the King of Bahrain".
