OL,6,FDuring the weekly business questions
OL,7,Fsession in Westminster on Thursday, Ms
OL,8,FBaxter told the Commons that "no-one"
OL,9,Ffrom the UK government would speak
OL,10,Fwith her about the case when Mr
OL,11,FHaggerty was in prison.
OL,13,FShe told MPs: "No-one would engage
OL,14,Fwith me to inform me of his welfare or
OL,15,Fthe current status of his case, and
OL,16,Fthat was because apparently I did not
OL,17,Fhave his explicit consent.
