OL,6,F"He was sitting in a jail in Bahrain.
OL,7,FI had his mother's consent. She was
OL,8,Falso a constituent, and yet still
OL,9,Fnobody would speak to me."
OL,11,FShe asked Commons Leader Lucy Powell:
OL,12,F"Can the Leader of the House ensure
OL,13,Fthat the FCDO (Foreign, Commonwealth
OL,14,Fand Development Office) work with me
OL,15,Fto arrange his urgent deportation back
OL,16,Fto this country, and that we avoid
OL,17,Ffurther delays in the future to MPs
OL,18,Fsecuring access to the information
OL,19,Fthey need to support their
OL,20,Fconstituents?"
